The facial assessment has been a huge part of my mentoring with @harley_academy and the key question "what bothers you the most?" can be very telling. When the practitioner sees lines, volume depletion, skin quality, facial proportions etc, the best person to communicate it, is usually the client themselves with phases such as "I just don't want to look tired all the time" or "people ask me why I always look angry"....which isn't usually a desired look...unless of course, you're @IceCube! Developing these consultation skills are one of the reasons I've loved my mentoring sessions with @harley_academy and gained so much from doing my Level 7 Qualification in Injectables with them.
